        Creates recipe with inputed data, and also generates unique UUID for access.
        Parameters:
        name - Title of recipe
        description - Description of recipe
        ingredients - List of ingredients required for recipe
        directions - Instructions on how to make recipe
        creatorEmail - Who created the recipe
        location - Whether recipe is a local or external recipe

      • Recipe

        public Recipe()
        Used when adding images to a recipe that has not been formally created yet. Be sure to generate a UUID to be used as the filename for photos.
